{"type": "article", "id": 35213, "title": "虽然不日常，但这套雨天骑行装也挺酷的｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-04T23:11:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 32650, "name": "YOU+MORE！"}, {"id": 35488, "name": "AANDERSSON"}, {"id": 35489, "name": "Ohhio"}, {"id": 35490, "name": "72 and Sunny"}, {"id": 34601, "name": "山中一宏"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161204221011Tn5vfkczytX3Q4jA.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Raynsie by 72 and Sunny</h3><p>提到荷兰，除了穿梭在大街小巷的自行车之外，这个国家还以它的多雨气候著名。来自阿姆斯特丹的创意公司 <a href=\"https://www.72andsunny.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">72 and Sunny</a> 最近就推出了为骑行者设计的雨衣产品 <a href=\"https://raynsie.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Raynsie</a>，虽然采用的是在穿脱上不算非常方便的连裤设计，但可以保护下身不被雨打湿。这些雨衣的另一个特点就是鲜艳的色彩搭配，加上反光条之后在雨夜之中显得相当抢眼。你可以通过它的<a href=\"https://raynsie.com/collections/raynsie-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买到这些雨衣，普通款和反光面料款售价分别为 299 和 350 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221029y2hGBS0zH8XdPAJM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221030p0zW9hGu5OvPCsS3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016120422103074NnIgjaUepR12Qc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221030KCtbuH3kzpiVhf8A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221030SBk8wWmYVpa7Hlos.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Shapes Collection by AANDERSSON</h3><p>美国费城的设计品牌 <a href=\"https://www.aandersson.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">AANDERSSON</a> 最近带来了一套像是雕塑装饰的马克杯系列 Shapes Collection。这些马克杯均采用陶土烧制而成，一部分保留了磨砂效果，另一部分则上有光滑的釉面。五款马克杯的手柄各不相同，呈现出简洁利落的几何美。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.aandersson.net/collections/all\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买到这五款杯子，售价为 24 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221053o2059l7BTRinN8xh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221052yrgxhiKQ1aXS2BDc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221052vMPe0xiFTqA5nRwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221052ak01ifuSvpbnEg2U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221053aF8uD57f6cR9JB32.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221053JDk5ZX8VS4txfHiR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>猫の舌のしまい忘れ あぶらとり紙 by YOU+MORE！</h3><p>那个曾经带来兔子收纳包的日本品牌 <a href=\"http://www.felissimo.co.jp/youmore/\" rel=\"nofollow\">YOU+MORE！</a>最近又将可爱的动物主题引入了常用物品当中，推出了以猫咪吐舌为造型的吸油面纸。猫咪所吐出的粉红色舌头实际上是面纸的末端，使用时只要轻轻一扯就可以取出了。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.felissimo.co.jp/youmore/wk57514/gcd695192/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，一包内有 30 张面纸，两包一组的套装价为 701 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612042211189kTxL35lQtij1wCf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221118129EBcyJ4AOZIvT5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221118JguealxofQUNkTzA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221119PyOalYVCdgic2LzN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ohhio Braid by Ohhio</h3><p>乌克兰设计工作室 <a href=\"http://ohhio.me/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ohhio</a> 此前专门经营用美丽诺羊毛（merino wool）编织的那些想让人埋进去的家居用品，当设计师们发现并没有类似美丽诺羊毛那样的材料后，他们决定亲手制作出一种既坚韧又柔软材料。Braid 就是 Ohhio 的研发成果，这种手工打造的材料内部采用的是硅酮处理过的微纤维（microfiber）填充物，无缝的棉质外层中还混合了棉纶以及氨纶，最终使整个材料具有相当高的柔韧性。Ohhio 目前推出的 Braid 产品既有附 DIY 指南的线团（分为三种长度），还有用 Braid 制作的成品，其中包括毯子、垫子和宠物用品。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1163965827/ohhio-braid-unique-craft-material-for-chunky-creat\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，产品价格从 19 到 498 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612042211415swTWcElXp63nL9C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221142yn0jOueDQrp8Ub3d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.107353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016120422114268iBceJzNGlHhXwR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221141nQB2NkhYZd8jp9CD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Collapsible moon by 山中一宏</h3><p>想在家中再现一轮明月又多了一种新形式。日本设计师<a href=\"http://www.kazuhiroyamanaka.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">山中一宏</a>最近以摄影使用的反光板为灵感，带来了一款名为 Collapsible moon 的折叠型灯具。山中在弹簧钢制成的框架边缘嵌入了向中央发光的 LED 灯带，打开后就形成了满月般的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221158ZPDmTHjoSefkybOd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634474\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221158KAFg804iZWa25jpM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221158nIyRrD9HQFBPXZOC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619804\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221158iw6ItJbWkjOvR897.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.358191\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Yosh by Anna Samoylova</h3><p>提到马桶刷，相信不少人都想着该怎么把它藏在隐蔽的角落。为了让人们不再把它视为一件丑陋的居家必备品，俄罗斯设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/12093485b5\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anna Samoylova</a> 带来了这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/45477987/Toilet-brush-Yosh\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yosh</a> 的概念设计。她打破常规，为马桶刷设计了纤细而且可以灵活调整的手柄，在将毛刷扁平化的同时还在底座周围也加入了一圈，两者结合可以让用户刷到平时难以触及的角落。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612042212202fP4o3ubHvXhIYGO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221220Xp9UfJvdI8e3FN4o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221220JNEaSsXbWgtRv2w5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161204221220dygvnWOwYTZsqLN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.982857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}